comments: Forbes (SAS) makes marginal contact to Martin's (CHA) side on his driving shot attempt.
Bridges (CHA) legally contests the shot attempt by DeRozan (SAS).
DeRozan (SAS) makes contact with Rozier's (CHA) head and affects his driving shot attempt.
Brdiges (CHA) places his hands momentarily to DeRozan's (SAS) arms and removes them without affecting his FOM.
Washington (CHA)  maintains a legal vertical position contesting the driving shot attempt by Gay (SAS) and absorbs the contact.
Rozier (CHA) places his hand to Lyles' (SAS) hip momentarily and removes it during his drive to the basket.
Gay (SAS) makes a slight brush to the top of Rozier's (CHA) head on his driving shot attempt.
Martin (CHA) is in the paint without actively guarding for longer than three seconds.
Bridges (CHA) makes incidental contact to DeRozan's (SAS) wrist after the release as he defends his driving shot attempt.
Lyles (SAS) engages with Martin (CHA) during the rebound and separate as he secures the loose ball.
Forbes (SAS) makes marginal contact to Rozier (CHA) at the end of his drive as he is making the pass.
